metadata.name: Silver Linings
metadata.description:
SILVER LININGS AIRDROP

In celebration of the one-year anniversary of selling my first NFT, this photograph, "Silver Linings," is an exclusive airdrop for my collectors who supported me through my first year of navigating this new space.

"Silver Linings" is a reminder that during these uncertain times we are living in, there is always a ray of hope or some positivity to be found, even in bad situations. To me, this photograph expresses positivity, optimism, and hope.

Edition of 117.
